DJI RS 2 is more than just a gimbal, it's an all-in-one filmmaking solution. So, we decided to partner with award-winning filmmaker @brandon_l_li for a new installment of DJI Film School. Watch as he takes a deep dive into camera movement and how it impacts the story you're trying to tell. 
•
#DJI #DJIRS2 #Ronin #Gimbal #Filmmaking
